---item_105 Chronoshift Marksman---
Type :: Gun
Slot :: Gun
Gun Definition :: [[Chronoshift Marksman]]
Rarity :: Exotic
Durability :: 5

Hits store bonus bullets. Last shot in clip fires all stored bullets. Misses reset bonus bullets.

Accuracy creates a cascade of chronoshifted projectiles.

---gundef_Chronoshift Marksman---
Fire Speed :: 1.0
Bullets In Chamber :: 5
Reload Speed :: 2.0
Sprite :: weapons_105
Fire Event :: rifleb
Reload Event :: riflereload
Bullet Definition :: [[chronoshift]]
Archetype :: LongRangeRifle
Muzzle VFX :: Muzzle 0.60
Fire Type :: SemiAuto
Bullet Lifetime :: 1.2
Innate Spikes :: [[Chronoshift]]

---bulletdef_chronoshift---
sprite Rifle14
color 3
potency 280
fire 40 relative -1 1

---spike_Chronoshift---
Auras :: [[Chronoshift]]

Each hit stores a bonus bullet. Last shot fires all bonus bullets. Misses reset bonus bullets.

---aura_Chronoshift---
Type :: Buff
Duration :: -1
Icon :: 
Max Stacks :: 1
Time Per Tick :: 1.0
Definitions :: [[Custom:Chronoshift]]

